<br>
Wow, Im impressed.<br>
<br>
Even when statue was fully debuffed I would still get plenty of partial resists and even a few full resists across the range of spell types.  I could have just been very unlucky.  We'll see how it goes next time. <p><p align=left><b>Yurimaru Manaburn </b><br>
